_struct.pdbx_model_details
;This model was generated unsupervised by the SWISS-MODEL homology-modelling pipeline for the SWISS-MODEL Repository, a database of annotated 3D protein structure models. The modelled monomer covers following UniProtKB entries:

  - P83104/ M3K7L_DROME, Putative mitogen-activated protein kinase kinase kinase 7-like

Estimated model accuracy of this model is 0.495, calculated by SWISS-MODEL as Global Model Quality Estimate (GMQE).
;
_struct.pdbx_structure_determination_methodology computational
_struct.title 'Model for UniProtKB entries P83104'
